v-on-Don]].<ref name=career>{{FootballFacts.ru|30084<!-- -cackin-emil-vasilevich -->}}</ref>\n\n==Honours==\n* [[Russian Premier League]] bronze: 1996.\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Tsatskin, Emil}}\n[[Category:1975 births]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Saint Petersburg]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Russian footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football forwards]]\n[[Category:Russian Premier League players]]\n[[Category:Russian expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Kazakhstan]]\n[[Category:FC Rotor Volgograd players]]\n[[Category:FC Rostov players]]\n[[Category:FC Dynamo Stavropol players]]\n[[Category:FC Kuban Krasnodar players]]\n[[Category:FC Luch Vladivostok players]]\n[[Category:FC Metallurg Lipetsk players]]\n[[Category:FC Volgar Astrakhan players]]\n[[Category:Russian expatriate sportspeople in Kazakhstan]]\n[[Category:FC Nika Krasny Sulin players]]\n[[Category:FC Taganrog players]]\n\n\n{{Russia-footy-forward-1970s-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox football biography\n| name= Emil Tsatskin\n| fullname = Emil Vasilyevich Tsatskin\n| image = \n| birth_date = {{birth date and age|1975|6|3|df=yes}} \n| birth_place = [[Saint Petersburg|Leningrad]], Russian SFSR\n| height = {{height|m=1.89}}\n| currentclub = \n| clubnumber = \n| position = [[Striker (association football)|Striker]]/[[Midfielder]]\n| youthyears1 = | youthclubs1 = [[FC Dinamo Sukhumi]]\n| youthyears2 = | youthclubs2 = RO UOR Rostov-on-Don\n| years1 = 1992\u20131993 \n| years2 = 1994\u20131995 \n| years3 = 1995 \n| years4 = 1996 \n| years5 = 1996 \n| years6 = 1997 \n| years7 = 1997\u20131999 \n| years8 = 2000\u20132002 \n| years9 = 2003 \n| years10 = 2003\u20132004 \n| years11 = 2005 \n| years12 = 2006\n| clubs1 = [[FC Rostselmash-d Rostov-on-Don]] \n| clubs2 = [[FC Metallurg Krasny Sulin]] \n| clubs3 = [[FC Torpedo Taganrog]] \n| clubs4 = [[FC Rotor Volgograd]] \n| clubs5 = [[FC Rostselmash Rostov-on-Don]] \n| clubs6 = [[FC Energiya Pyatigorsk]